4:
I knew that you people were very stubborn;
\q2 I knew that your heads were as hard as iron or brass.
\q1

17:
This is what Yahweh, the one who saves you, the Holy God of us Israelites, says:
\q2 "I am Yahweh, your God;
\q1 I teach you what is important for you to prosper;
\q2 I direct you and lead you to do the things that you should do.
\q1
